#. <section class="sutta" id="sn6.8"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn6.8:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 6"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 6"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn6.8:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "1. The Appeal"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 8. Katamodakatissasutta → katamorakatissasuttaṃ (bj) | tissakasuttaṃ (s1-3) | tissako (pts1)
msgctxt "sn6.8:0.3"
msgid "8. Katamodakatissasutta"
msgstr "8. About Katamorakatissaka"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.8:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn6.8:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā divāvihāragato hoti paṭisallīno."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time the Buddha had retreated to solitude for the day’s "
"meditation."

msgctxt "sn6.8:1.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho subrahmā ca paccekabrahmā suddhāvāso ca paccekabrahmā yena bhagavā "
"tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā paccekaṃ dvārabāhaṃ nissāya aṭṭhaṃsu."
msgstr ""
"Then the independent brahmās Subrahmā and Suddhāvāsa went to the Buddha and "
"stationed themselves one by each door-post."

#. VAR: katamodakatissakaṃ → katamorakatissaṃ (bj) | katamorakatissakaṃ (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn6.8:1.4"
msgid ""
"Atha kho suddhāvāso paccekabrahmā katamodakatissakaṃ bhikkhuṃ ārabbha "
"bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"Then Suddhāvāsa recited this verse about the mendicant Katamorakatissaka in "
"the Buddha’s presence:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.149"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.8:2.1"
msgid "“Appameyyaṃ paminanto,"
msgstr "“What wise person here would judge"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.8:2.2"
msgid "Kodha vidvā vikappaye;"
msgstr "the immeasurable by measuring them?"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.8:2.3"
msgid "Appameyyaṃ pamāyinaṃ,"
msgstr "I think anyone who’d do such a thing"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.8:2.4"
msgid "Nivutaṃ taṃ maññe akissavan”ti."
msgstr "must be a fool, wrapped in darkness.”"
